headline: Is Jabil’s 49% 2025 Rally Justified After Streamlining Operations?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your Jabil shares right now? You are not alone. With the stock closing at $212.44 and boasting a return of nearly 49% year to date, it is no wonder a lot of investors are wondering if the ride still has room to run. Jabil's numbers tell a story of impressive growth, especially over the longer haul, with a 71% jump in the last year and a staggering 555% over the past five years.
